🎢 Erlebe wilde Fahrgeschäfte & Jahrmarktsstimmung
🎮 tritt in Spielen basierend auf realen Attraktionen gegeneinander an
🍺 jage andere in Barrel Hunt
💀 kämpfe im Koop gegen Geister in Haunting Grounds
🐾 adoptiere & entwickle süße Haustiere
🧍‍♂️ gestalte deinen Avatar

Hol deine Freunde – hier ist immer was los! 

👉 Tritt unserer Community bei bit.ly/OktoberfestVRDiscord

🐾 Adopte & fais évoluer de mignons animaux de compagnie
🧍‍♂️ Personnalise ton avatar

Invite tes amis – ici, il se passe toujours quelque chose !

¡Entra al Oktoberfest, la feria social en VR llena de diversión para todos!

🎢 Súbete a emocionantes atracciones y disfruta del ambiente típico de un parque temático
🎮 Compite con otros en juegos multijugador basados en atracciones reales
🍺 Prueba el nuevo juego Barrel Hunt para una diversión al estilo “pilla-pilla”
💀 Haz equipo para un combate cooperativo y espeluznante en Haunting Grounds
🐾 Adopta adorables mascotas

Step into Oktoberfest, the social VR fun fair packed with fun for everyone!

🎢 Hop on wild rides and enjoy a typical theme park atmosphere
🎮 Compete with others in multiplayer games based on real attractions
🍺 Try the new Barrel Hunt game for tag-like fun

Grab your friends - there’s always something happening at Oktoberfest!

Join the community: bit.ly/OktoberfestVR

Погрузитесь в Oktoberfest — социальную VR-ярмарку, полную веселья для всех!

🎢 Катайтесь на безумных аттракционах и наслаждайтесь атмосферой парка развлечений
🎮 Соревнуйтесь с другими в многопользовательских играх, основанных на реальных аттракционах
🍺 Попробуйте новую игру Barrel Hunt для весёлых игр в салочки
💀 Объединяйтесь для жутких кооперативных сражений в Haunting Grounds
🐾 Заводите милых питомцев
🧍‍♂️ Кастомизируйте аватар и демонстрируйте свой стиль

nodes.long_description:
The world's most famous and oldest folk festival - the Munich Oktoberfest - is all about fun and socializing. Munich Oktoberfest - The Official Game brings these aspects into virtual reality as the worlds first social VR fun fair. Here it is possible to explore a virtual version of the festival together with friends and players from all over the world.

Join the virtual Oktoberfest to interact with other players, play hilarious multiplayer games and experience the true atmosphere of the Oktoberfest. Have fun working as a beer hall employee to earn your place in the hall of fame as quickest bartender or experience the spectacular motion rides together with your friends.

Of course authentic dressing in Bavarian costumes for your virtual Oktoberfest visit is also possible! So get your Lederhosen or Drindl ready and join the fun today!
